She told me to give
the bracelet to my wife,

14:11.092 --> 14:12.303
and I was explaining
right afterwards...

14:12.327 --> 14:13.471
I said my girlfriend...

14:13.495 --> 14:14.805
<font color="#80ff80">JAY:</font> Sit down, just breathe.
